data.description: Welcome to this charming 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo nestled in the desirable Bixby Knolls neighborhood of Long Beach. This home offers a comfortable and inviting living space. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, providing an ideal setting for both entertaining and daily living.    The kitchen is equipped with ample counter space, making it a delightful space for cooking and preparing meals. The master bedroom features an en-suite bathroom for added convenience and privacy. The second bedroom is spacious and versatile, suitable for guests, a home office, or a personal retreat.    Enjoy the Southern California sunshine on your private balcony, perfect for morning coffee or evening relaxation. The condo complex offer amenities such landscaped grounds, providing residents with a comfortable and enjoyable living experience.    Located in Bixby Knolls, you'll have easy access to local shops, restaurants, and parks. The area is known for its tree-lined streets and a sense of community. With proximity to major transportation routes, commuting to nearby areas is convenient.    Don't miss the opportunity to make this Bixby Knolls condo your new home – a place where comfort and convenience come together in the heart of Long Beach.
